title: Howls Moving Castle Papercraft.pdf
description:
Product Description
This item is a paper craft book.  
From the newest Studio Ghibli film, "Howl's Moving Castle", Kodansha brings us an actual papercraft model of the magical moving castle itself! Excellent detail all over, carefully researched; you'll need a steady hand, sharp scissors, clear tape and white glue, to assemble this many-layered beauty. 51 two-sided pages of papercraft "parts" (that's a lotta parts!), plus instructions. 


This book was pretty easy to follow the instructions even though I can't read or write Japanese.
